                                    "header":  "Opportunity description",
                                    "body":  "\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"description\"\u003e\u003carticle data-scroll-anchor=\"true\" data-testid=\"conversation-turn-92\" data-turn=\"assistant\" data-turn-id=\"65868bbe-3bdd-4f22-be69-c74a943c39f3\" dir=\"auto\" tabindex=\"-1\"\u003e\u003cdiv tabindex=\"-1\"\u003e\u003cdiv data-message-author-role=\"assistant\" data-message-id=\"243fd7d2-1054-4542-9903-dd3d3b4305b5\" data-message-model-slug=\"gpt-5-2\" dir=\"auto\"\u003e\u003cp data-end=\"348\" data-start=\"0\"\u003eThe \u003cstrong data-end=\"60\" data-start=\"4\"\u003eUniversity of Science and Technology of China (USTC)\u003c/strong\u003e offers international programs taught in \u003cstrong data-end=\"112\" data-start=\"101\"\u003eEnglish\u003c/strong\u003e in the fields of \u003cstrong data-end=\"157\" data-start=\"130\"\u003escience and engineering\u003c/strong\u003e. The university is known for the \u003cstrong data-end=\"229\" data-start=\"191\"\u003ehighest academic standards in Asia\u003c/strong\u003e. The International College was established to attract talented students and provide a leading educational environment.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-end=\"386\" data-start=\"350\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-end=\"384\" data-start=\"350\"\u003eFunding and Financial Benefits\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul data-end=\"679\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\" data-start=\"387\"\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"414\" data-start=\"387\"\u003e\u003cp data-end=\"414\" data-start=\"389\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-end=\"412\" data-start=\"389\"\u003eTuition fee waiver.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"454\" data-start=\"415\"\u003e\u003cp data-end=\"454\" data-start=\"417\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-end=\"452\" data-start=\"417\"\u003eComprehensive health insurance.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"502\" data-start=\"455\"\u003e\u003cp data-end=\"502\" data-start=\"457\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-end=\"477\" data-start=\"457\"\u003eResearch funding\u003c/strong\u003e for graduate students.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"679\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-start=\"503\"\u003e\u003cp data-end=\"552\" data-start=\"505\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-end=\"524\" data-start=\"505\"\u003eMonthly stipend\u003c/strong\u003e (amount varies by level):\u003c/p\u003e\u003col class=\"kh\" data-end=\"679\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-start=\"555\"\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"600\" data-start=\"555\"\u003e\u003cp data-end=\"600\" data-start=\"557\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-end=\"570\" data-start=\"557\"\u003e2,500 RMB\u003c/strong\u003e for undergraduate students.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"643\" data-start=\"603\"\u003e\u003cp data-end=\"643\" data-start=\"605\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-end=\"618\" data-start=\"605\"\u003e3,000 RMB\u003c/strong\u003e for master\u0026rsquo;s students.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"679\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-start=\"646\"\u003e\u003cp data-end=\"679\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-start=\"648\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-end=\"661\" data-start=\"648\"\u003e3,500 RMB\u003c/strong\u003e for PhD students.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ol\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/article\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e"
                                },
